OL,3,CHow much for a beach hut with no
OL,4,Cwater, loos or phone signal?
OL,6,FBeach hut enthusiasts explain to ITV
OL,7,FMeridian's John Ryall why most at
OL,8,FHerne Bay remain unsold.
OL,10,FHow much would you pay for a beach
OL,11,Fhut? In some parts of the South East,
OL,12,Fthey can fetch a pretty price, well
OL,13,Fover $50,000.
OL,15,FCash-strapped Canterbury City Council
OL,16,Fdecided to build some at Herne Bay to
OL,17,Fboost their coffers but it's not quite
OL,18,Fgone according to plan.
