OL,3,CHow much for a beach hut with no
OL,4,Cwater, loos or phone signal?
OL,6,FWhen Canterbury City Council saw its
OL,7,Ffinances heading for the red it
OL,8,Fdecided it was time for some blue-sky
OL,9,Fthinking.
OL,11,FThirty beach huts were built at Herne
OL,12,FBay, for sale at #30,000 each, which
OL,13,Fwould net the city council hundreds of
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds in profit.
