OL,3,CHow much for a beach hut with no
OL,4,Cwater, loos or phone signal?
OL,6,FThe trouble is they're not the most
OL,7,Fcolourful or characterful beach huts.
OL,8,FThey're also some way from town, there
OL,9,Fare no amenities, no loos and no fresh
OL,10,Fwater. And if you fancy using one for
OL,11,Fa cheeky work from home day, there's
OL,12,Fno phone signal.
OL,14,FAndrew Cook from the Herne Bay Beach
OL,15,FHut Association said they're missing
OL,16,Fsome essential facilities.
