OL,3,CHow much for a beach hut with no
OL,4,Cwater, loos or phone signal?
OL,6,F"It needs to have loos for it and CCTV
OL,7,Fand of course they do need to have
OL,8,Fwater there as well, which Im sure the
OL,9,Fcouncil will get round to but they
OL,10,Fneed to actually get on and do it now."
OL,12,FOther beach huts on this coast, like
OL,13,Fthose at Tankerton, fetch north of
OL,14,F#60,000. But most at Herne Bay look
OL,15,Fset to end the summer unsold.
OL,17,FEstate agent, Thomas Dean, said, "The
OL,18,Flocation isn't the best but you can
OL,19,Fget over that if the price is right
OL,20,Fand the price would be I reckon around
OL,21,Fabout #20,000."
