OL,3,CHow much for a beach hut with no
OL,4,Cwater, loos or phone signal?
OL,6,FPolitical control at Canterbury City
OL,7,FCouncil has changed since this fund-
OL,8,Fraising scheme was hatched.
OL,10,F"It's not a great time in the beach
OL,11,Fhut market generally," said Cllr Chris
OL,12,FCornell, Canterbury City Council.
OL,14,F"Even if you look at private sales
OL,15,Fthey're slowing and they have been
OL,16,Fslow for the past 12 months or so."
