OL,3,CHow much for a beach hut with no
OL,4,Cwater, loos or phone signal?
OL,6,F"I'd expect the market to pick up a
OL,7,Flittle bit but I think after the
OL,8,Fbudget cycle we'll review the price."
OL,9,FSo, nice view, but so far no prospect
OL,10,Fof a profit from this not so desirable
OL,11,Fresidence.
